queries.question: Count the number of active customers
queries.query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM customer WHERE active = 1;

queries.question: Show details of customer with email 'MARY.SMITH@sakilacustomer.org'
List first and last names of all customers sorted by last name
queries.query: SELECT first_name, last_name FROM customer ORDER BY last_name;

queries.question: How many inactive customers are there?
queries.query: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM customer WHERE active = 0;

queries.question: Find all customers associated with store ID 1
Show the top 5 most recently updated customer records
queries.query: SELECT * FROM customer ORDER BY last_update DESC LIMIT 5;

queries.question: Find first 5 active customers
queries.query: SELECT * FROM customer WHERE active = 1 ORDER BY customer_id ASC LIMIT 5;
